Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}道格{\r}\NDoug?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}親愛的 你還好吧{\r}\NHoney, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你又做夢了 道格{\r}\NYou were dreaming. Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是否又是關於火星的夢{\r}\NWas it about Mars?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}好點沒{\r}\NIs that better?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我可憐的寶貝{\r}\NMy poor baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這些夢都快佔據你的腦袋了{\r}\NThis is getting to be an obsession.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}她也在夢裡嗎{\r}\NWas she there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}誰{\r}\NWho?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那個你對我提過的褐髮女子{\r}\NThe one you told me about. The brunette.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}羅莉{\r}\NOh, Lori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我不敢相信連我作夢你也會吃醋{\r}\NI can't believe you're jealous of a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 她到底是誰  - 無足輕重的人{\r}\N- Who is she?  - Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}無足輕重的人 她叫什麼名字{\r}\N"Nobody"? What's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我不知道{\r}\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 告訴我  - 我不知道啊{\r}\N- Tell me!  - I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你最好告訴我{\r}\NYou better tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這可不好笑 道格 你每天晚上都夢到她啊{\r}\NIt's not funny, Doug. You dream about her every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}但我到了早上總會回到你身邊{\r}\NAnd I'm always back in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}放開我{\r}\NLet me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別這樣 寶貝{\r}\NCome on, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你知道你才是我夢想中的女孩{\r}\NYou know you're the girl of my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你這是真心話{\r}\NYou mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你很清楚我是真心的{\r}\NYou know I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}讓我給你的春夢提供些題材{\r}\NI'll give you something to dream about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}主席為這次攻擊辯護 宣稱在太空中佈署的武器{\r}\NThe chairman defended the attack, saying that space-based weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是唯一能對付南區新興勢力的有效防禦{\r}\Nare our only defence against the southern block's numerical superiority.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}此外 火星昨晚又發生暴亂{\r}\NAnd more violence last night on Mars
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}要求獨立的恐怖份子{\r}\Nwhere terrorists demanding independence
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}再度迫使T礦的開採停工{\r}\Nonce again halted the extraction of terbinium ore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}寡頭和他率領的所謂自由戰土{\r}\NKuato and his so-called freedom brigade
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}宣稱這次爆炸事件是他們幹的{\r}\Nclaimed credit for this latest bombing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}企圖重新開啟已封閉的金字塔形礦坑{\r}\Nwhich attempted to reopen the sealed-off Pyramid Mines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}火星軍事當局僅以最少的兵力就恢復當地秩序{\r}\NMars military restored order with minimal use of force
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}所有重要的戰略設施都在一小時內修復完畢{\r}\Nand all damage to the strategic facility was repaired within hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不准拍攝{\r}\NNo cameras!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}目前已經有一處礦坑關閉 火星行政官維羅斯·柯黑根{\r}\NWith one mine already closed, Mars administrator Vilos Cohaagen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}宣稱在必要時仍將動用軍隊{\r}\Nvowed that troops would be used if necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}以維持足額的開採量{\r}\Nto keep production at full capacity...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}難怪你會做惡夢 你老喜歡看新聞{\r}\NNo wonder you're having nightmares. You're always watching the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 羅莉  - 道格{\r}\N- Lori.  - Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 咱們就這麼辦吧  - 做什麼{\r}\N- Let's do it.  - Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}搬到火星去住{\r}\NMove to Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你為什麼一定要破壞一個如此美好的早晨呢{\r}\NHoney, why do you have to spoil a perfectly wonderful morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}考慮一下吧{\r}\NJust think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}親愛的 我們已經談過無數次了 你會討厭住在火星上的{\r}\NSweetheart, we've been through this a million times. You'd hate it on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那裡既乾燥 醜陋 又無趣{\r}\NIt's dry, it's ugly, it's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}更何況 那裡隨時都可能爆發革命{\r}\NI mean, really, a revolution could break out there any second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}柯黑根說那只是一小撮偏激份子{\r}\NCohaagen says it's just a few extremists.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你相信他的說法{\r}\NYou believe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}好吧 就當我沒提過此事{\r}\NOK. Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}絕對不行 火星是北區投下大量經費才殖民成功的{\r}\NAbsolutely not. Mars was colonised by the northern block at enormous expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們全部的軍費都得依賴此地的T礦開採{\r}\NOur entire war effort depends on their terbinium.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}就只因為一些懶惰的變種人而將這一切放棄是荒唐的想法{\r}\NIt's ridiculous to think we'd give it away just because some lazy mutants...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}道格{\r}\NDoug
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 或許咱們該去做一次旅行  - 羅莉 拜託別擋住銀幕{\r}\N- Maybe we should take a trip.  - Lori, move, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}還有許多比火星更好的地方啊{\r}\NThere's a lot better places than Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}土星怎樣 你不想到土星去看看嗎{\r}\NWhat about Saturn? Don't you wanna see Saturn?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}大家都說那裡好漂亮{\r}\NEverybody says that its gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}事實是寡頭先生和他的恐怖份子企圖散佈這些謠言{\r}\NFact is, it's Mr Kuato and his terrorists who spread these rumours
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}以損害人民對政府的信任{\r}\Nto undermine trust in the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們可以做一次長途太空之旅{\r}\NWe could take a long space cruise,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那種無須刻意做任何事的旅行{\r}\Nthe kind with nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你們找到寡頭了嗎  - 我們還不知道他長什麼樣{\r}\N- Have you found Kuato yet?  - We don't even know what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你說什麼  - 我快遲到了 羅莉{\r}\N- What do you say?  - I'm late, Lori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}親愛的 道格{\r}\NSweetheart. Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我知道剛搬到一個新城市是很難適應的{\r}\NI know it's hard being in a new town,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}但請你試試看 好嗎{\r}\Nbut let's give it a chance, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}羅莉 你難道不明白嗎{\r}\NLori, don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我覺得我這輩子不該只是如此{\r}\NI feel like I was meant for something more than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我想在我的一生中有番作為 我想成為一個有用的人{\r}\NI want to do something with my life. I want to be somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你已經是個了不起的人了{\r}\NYou are somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你是我愛的男人{\r}\NYou're the man I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}再見{\r}\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}祝你有個愉快的一天{\r}\NHave a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你現在正進入一個安全地帶{\r}\NYou are now entering a safety zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}所有經核准的武器 都不得攜出檢查點{\r}\NNo unauthorised weapons allowed beyond this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你現在正進入一個安全地帶{\r}\NYou are now entering a safety zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}所有未經核准的武器 都不得攜出檢查點{\r}\NNo unauthorised weapons allowed beyond this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你是否夢想到雪地去滑雪 但卻苦無門路{\r}\NWould you like to ski but you're snowed under with work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你是否夢想到海底悠遊...{\r}\NDo you dream of a vacation at the bottom of the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}卻付不起旅費{\r}\Nbut you can't float the bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:10:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你是否渴望到火星上爬山...{\r}\NHave you always wanted to climb the mountains of Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}但你的體力卻已經走下坡{\r}\N...but now you're over the hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那就到瑞可公司來吧{\r}\NThen come to Recall Incorporated
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你在此可以買到你心目中理想的假期{\r}\Nwhere you can buy the memory of your ideal vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}比真正的旅遊經驗更便宜 更安全 更好{\r}\Ncheaper, safer and better than the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別讓美好的人生從你眼前溜過{\r}\NSo don't let life pass you by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}立刻撥電話到瑞可來{\r}\NCall Recall for the memory of a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}給你的生命留下美好的回憶{\r}\NFor the memory of a lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}瑞可...{\r}\NRecall, Recall, Recall
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}哈利{\r}\NHarry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你聽過瑞可這個公司吧  - 瑞可{\r}\N- Harry! You ever hear of Recall?  - Recall?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}就是專門賣假記憶的地方{\r}\NWhere they sell those fake memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是啊 瑞可 瑞可...{\r}\NOh, Recall! Recall, recall, recall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你想去找他們  - 我不知道 或許吧{\r}\N- Thinking of going there?  - I don't know. Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 別去  - 為什麼{\r}\N- Well, don't.  - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我有一個朋友試了他們的特殊產品 結果腦前葉被切除了{\r}\NA friend of mine tried one of their special offers, nearly got himself lobotomised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}真的{\r}\NNo shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別拿自己腦袋開玩笑 兄弟 不值得{\r}\NDon't fuck with your brain, pal. It ain't worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我想是吧{\r}\NI guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你好{\r}\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}下午好 歡迎光臨瑞可公司{\r}\NGood afternoon. Welcome to Recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我是道格拉斯·奎德 和醫生約好了{\r}\NDouglas Quaid. I have an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 鮑伯  - 是的{\r}\N- Bob?  - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 道格·奎德來找你了  - 我馬上來{\r}\N- Doug Quaid is here to see you.  - I'll be right out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}好{\r}\NOK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}請稍待一下 奎德先生{\r}\NThat'll be just one minute, Mr Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}謝謝你{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 道格 我是鮑伯·麥克連 幸會  - 幸會{\r}\N- Doug! Bob McClane. Good to see you.  - Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}到裡面談吧 這邊請{\r}\NCome on in. Through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}坐 不必拘束{\r}\NGo and have a seat. Make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}謝謝你{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}告訴我 道格{\r}\NNow, help me out here, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你想要植入的記憶是關於...  - 火星{\r}\N- You were interested in a memory of...  - Of Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是啊 火星...{\r}\NYeah. Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}有困難嗎{\r}\NIs there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我老實告訴你好了 如果你對外太空感興趣的話{\r}\NTo be perfectly honest with you, Doug, if outer space is your thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我想你會更喜歡我們的土星之旅{\r}\Nyou'd be much happier with one of our Saturn cruises.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這是目前最流行的{\r}\NEverybody raves about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不 我對土星沒興趣 我要的是火星{\r}\NNo. I'm not interested in Saturn. I said Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}好吧 花錢的人是大爺{\r}\NOK. You're the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那麼就設定在火星{\r}\NMars it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我看看...{\r}\NNow, let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}一次標準的火星之旅 收費是899個信用單位{\r}\NThe basic Mars package will run you 899 credits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這包括整整兩個禮拜的記憶 不但完整 而且非常詳細{\r}\NNow, that's for two full weeks of memories, complete in every detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}如果你要更久的時間就得再加錢 因為我們得植入更深{\r}\NIf you want a longer trip, that'll cost you more cos it's a deeper implant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}兩個禮拜的旅程裡包括什麼{\r}\NWhat's in the two-week package?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}首先 當你到瑞可來{\r}\NFirst of all, let me tell you. When you go Recall,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}所得到的絕對是第一流的記憶{\r}\Nyou get nothing but first-class memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}在太空梭上接有私人包廂{\r}\NPrivate cabin on the shuttle,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}住宿希爾頓的豪華套房 加上到所有觀光點遊覽{\r}\Ndeluxe suite at the Hilton, all the major sights:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}金字塔山 大運河 當然還有維納斯城{\r}\NMount Pyramid, the Grand Canals and of course, Venusville.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}但這些記憶將有多逼真{\r}\NBut how real does it seem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 和你自己的記憶一樣逼真  - 少來 別忽悠我了{\r}\N- As real as any memory in your head.  - Come on. Don't bullshit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我是說真的 你的大腦將分不出它有何差別{\r}\NNo. I'm telling you, Doug. Your brain will not know the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}信用保證 不滿意可以退錢{\r}\NAnd that's guaranteed or your money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}被你們切除腦前葉的那傢伙呢{\r}\NWhat about the guy you lobotomised?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你們事後有退錢給他嗎{\r}\NDid he get a refund?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這是好久以前的事了{\r}\NYou're talking ancient history.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}在今天 以瑞可的方式旅行 比搭火箭安全多了{\r}\NNowadays, travelling with Recall is safer than getting on a rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你看看那些統計數字{\r}\NCheck out those statistics.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}更何況 一次真正的旅程再麻煩不過了{\r}\NBesides, a real holiday is a pain in the butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你會遺失行李 碰上壞天氣 還會被計程車司機敲竹槓{\r}\NYou got lost luggage, lousy weather, crooked taxi drivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}但當你以瑞可的方式旅行時 一切都是完美的{\r}\NWhen you travel with Recall, everything is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你說怎樣{\r}\NSo, what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 好吧  - 明智的決定{\r}\N- All right.  - Smart move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}好 在你填這份調查表的同時{\r}\NAll right, while you fill out this questionnaire,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我順便向你介紹一下其他的產品{\r}\NI'm going to familiarise you with some of our options.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不要其他的產品{\r}\NNo options.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}隨便你好了 我能問你一個問題嗎{\r}\NWhatever you say. Can I ask you just one question?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}在你以往每次的旅行中{\r}\NWhat is that is exactly the same
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}都有哪一樣共同點{\r}\Nabout every single vacation you have ever taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我放棄{\r}\NI give UP
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你 你就是那共同點{\r}\NYou. You're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不論你到哪裡去 你總是同一個你{\r}\NNo matter where you go, there you are. It's always the same old you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我建議你這回暫且不當你自己{\r}\NLet me suggest that you take a vacation from yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我知道這聽來很玄{\r}\NI know, it sounds wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這是我們最新的旅行方式 我們稱它叫"自我旅行"{\r}\NIt is the latest thing in travel. We call it the Ego Trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不 我對這沒有興趣{\r}\NNo. I'm not interested in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你會喜歡它的 道格{\r}\NYou're gonna love this, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們提供你以不同的身份去旅行{\r}\NWe offer you a choice of alternate identities during your trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}幹嘛以觀光客的身份到火星去 你可以花花公子的身份去{\r}\NWhy go to Mars as a tourist, when you can go as a playboy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 或是著名的運動員 或...  - "秘密情報員"{\r}\N- Or a famous jock or...?  - "Secret agent."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這要多少錢{\r}\NHow much is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}讓我來對你詳細解說一下{\r}\NA-ha! Let me tantalise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你是個第一流的情報員 喬裝臥底執行你最重要的任務{\r}\NYou are a top operative under deep cover on your most important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}黑白兩道的人馬都在追殺你{\r}\NPeople are trying to kill you. Left and right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}美麗的異國情調的女人{\r}\NYou meet this beautiful, exotic woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}說下去{\r}\NGo on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我不想破壞你到時候享受的樂趣{\r}\NI don't wanna spoil it for you, Doug,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}但我向你保證 在旅程結束時{\r}\Nbut by the time the trip is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你將獲得美人的芳心 殺光壞人 拯救整個星球{\r}\Nyou get the girl, kill the bad guys and save the entire planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你說說看 這不值得花三百個信用單位嗎{\r}\NNow, you tell me. Isn't that worth a measly 300 credits?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 這是你的第一次旅行  - 嗯{\r}\N- Your first trip?  - Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別擔心 咱們這裡很少出差錯的{\r}\NWell, don't worry. Things hardly ever fuck up around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}晚安 道格{\r}\NGood evening... Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我是樓醫生  - 幸會{\r}\N- I'm Dr Lull.  - Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}厄尼 連結第62B及37號的細胞問質{\r}\NErnie, patch in matrix 62-B-37.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}還有 你想增加些外星怪物嗎{\r}\NAnd would you like us to integrate some alien stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}好啊 有何不可{\r}\NSure. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 雙頭怪物  - 你從來不看新聞嗎{\r}\N- Two-headed monsters?  - Don't you keep up with the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們現在研究外星人的史前古跡{\r}\NWe're doing alien artefacts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}看起來真古怪{\r}\NIt's wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是啊 它們有數百萬年的歷史{\r}\NYeah, they date back a million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 厄尼  - 這玩意是新的{\r}\N- Ernie?  - That's a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 火星上的藍色天空  - 結婚很久了{\r}\N- Blue sky on Mars.  - Been married long?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 八年了  - 噢 我明白了{\r}\N- Eight years.  - Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}背著老婆出來找些刺激{\r}\NSlipping away for a little hanky-panky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 不完全是 我一直對火星感興趣  - 系統運行{\r}\N- No. I'm fascinated with Mars.  - All systems go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們可以開始了{\r}\NThen we're set.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}準備進入夢鄉了{\r}\NReady for dreamland?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}首先我要問你幾個問題 這樣我們才能適當調整自我之旅{\r}\NI'll be asking you some questions so we can fine-tune the Ego program.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你若能老實回答 你的旅程就會更加愉快{\r}\NYou answer honestly, you'll enjoy yourself a whole lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你的性活動傾向是什麼  - 異性{\r}\N- Your sexual orientation.  - Hetero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}好 你喜歡什麼樣的女人{\r}\NSo, how do you like your women?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}金髮的 褐髮的 紅發的{\r}\NBlonde? Brunette? Redhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}褐髮的{\r}\NBrunette.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}苗條的運動員型 肉感型{\r}\NSlim. Athletic. Voluptuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}運動員型{\r}\NAthletic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}端莊型 侵略型 輕佻型{\r}\NDemure. Aggressive. Sleazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 老實回答  - 輕佻型{\r}\N- Be honest.  - Sleazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}端莊型{\r}\NDemure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}41A 厄尼{\r}\N41A, Ernie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他將度過一段狂野的時光{\r}\NBoy, is he gonna have a wild time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 他會不想回來  - 這是一定的{\r}\N- He's not gonna want to come back.  - Oh, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那麼...{\r}\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你說呢{\r}\Nwhat do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我難以決定 連個紀念品也沒有{\r}\NI'm not so sure, and I don't get a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}也不儘然 你只要加些額外費用{\r}\NNot true. For just a few more credits
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們就提供T恤 以及你在觀光點拍的照片{\r}\Nwe supply T-shirts, snapshots of you at the site,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}甚至信件...{\r}\Nand even letters from...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 什麼事  - 你最好快來這邊一下{\r}\N- What is it?  - You'd better get down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我正在和一個重要客戶談生意{\r}\NI am with a very important client.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}看來咱們又碰上另一個精神分裂症患者{\r}\NLooks like we got another schizoid embolism.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我馬上回來  - 麥克連先生{\r}\N- I'll be right back.  - Uh... Mr McClane?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 麥克連先生  - 鮑伯 出了什麼事{\r}\N- Mr McClane?  - Bob! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別讓她走掉{\r}\NDon't let her leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}滾開{\r}\NGet off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你們暴露了我的身份{\r}\NYou blew my cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你連個簡單的植入手術都做不好{\r}\NWhat's going on? You can't do a simple goddamn double implant?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不是我的錯 他的記憶有問題{\r}\NIt's not my fault we hit a memory cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他們隨時會到 他們會殺了你們{\r}\NThey'll be here any minute! They'll kill you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 他在說些什麼  - 放開我{\r}\N- What is he talking about?  - Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}奎德先生 試著冷靜下來{\r}\NMr Quaid, try to calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我的名字不叫奎德{\r}\NMy name is not Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 讓我走 快替我鬆綁  - 厄尼 抓住他的腿{\r}\N- Let me go! Untie me now!  - Ernie, grab his leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 放開我  - 快拉住他{\r}\N- Untie me!  - Hold him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}放開我{\r}\NLet me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你沒事吧{\r}\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}聽我說 他一直不停地說著火星的事{\r}\NListen to me. He's been going on and on about Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 他真的到過那裡  - 用你的腦袋想想 你這笨女人{\r}\N- He has really been there.  - Use your head, you dumb bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他剛剛的表現正是自我旅行中的情報員角色{\r}\NHe's just acting out the "secret agent" portion of his ego trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 這恐怕是不可能的  - 為什麼{\r}\N- I'm afraid that's not possible.  - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}因為我們根本還沒將記憶植入{\r}\NBecause we haven't implanted it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}慘了{\r}\NOh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這下可慘了{\r}\NOh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這正是我要告訴你的 有人洗掉了他的記憶{\r}\NI've been trying to tell you, someone has erased his memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}對不起 你是說"某人"{\r}\NExcuse me. "Someone"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們在談論該死的情報機構{\r}\NWe're talking about the fucking Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 閉嘴  - 鮑伯 那個客戶走了{\r}\N- Shut up!  - Bob, the client's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}好 好 聽我說 咱們就這麼辦{\r}\NOK, all right. All right, look. Here's what we're going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們將他所有關於瑞可的記憶通通洗掉{\r}\NRenata, cover up any memory he's got of us or Recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我盡力而為 他的記憶亂成一團{\r}\NI'll do what I can. It's pretty messy in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}厄尼 把他搬下去 送上計程車 蒂凡妮 你幫他{\r}\NErnie, dump him in a cab around the corner. Tiffany, you help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我要毀掉他的資料 退回他的錢{\r}\NI'm gonna destroy his file and refund his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}如果有人找上門來 就說我們從沒聽過道格·奎德{\r}\NAnd if anybody comes asking, we never heard of Douglas Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我在哪裡{\r}\NWhere am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:21:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你在一輛強尼計程車上  - 我怎麼會在這裡{\r}\N- You're in a Johnnycab.  - What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}對不起 你能換個方式問這問題嗎{\r}\NI'm sorry. Would you please rephrase the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我怎麼會坐上這輛計程車{\r}\NHow did I get in this taxi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}車門打開 你就上了車{\r}\NThe door opened, you got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}累了一天 是吧{\r}\NHell of a day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 這裡可以吧  - 停在這邊{\r}\N- This OK?  - Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 多謝你搭乘強尼計程車  - 謝謝你{\r}\N- Thank you for taking Johnnycab.  - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}希望你滿意我們的服務{\r}\NHope you enjoyed the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}嗨 奎德{\r}\NHey, Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 哈利  - 你的火星之旅如何{\r}\N- Harry.  - How was your trip to Mars?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.41,0:21:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 什麼旅行  - 你到瑞可公司去 還記得吧{\r}\N- What trip?  - You went to Recall. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我有嗎  - 是的 你去了{\r}\N- I did?  - Yeah, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.04,0:21:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我叫你別去 但你偏要去  - 你是誰 我爸爸{\r}\N- I told you not to, but you went anyway.  - What are you, my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 來吧 我請你喝一杯  - 聽著 我已晚到家了 謝謝你{\r}\N- Come on, I'll buy you a drink.  - Listen. I'm already late. Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}好 帶上他... 快點{\r}\NOK, bring him... Come on, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}咱們這就去喝一杯 快{\r}\NLet's go get that drink. Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.37,0:22:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這到底是怎麼回事 我到底做錯了什麼{\r}\NWhat the hell is going on? What the fuck did I do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.91,0:22:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 告訴我啊  - 你亂說關於火星的事{\r}\N- Tell me!  - You blabbed about Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你瘋了嗎 我對火星一無所知啊{\r}\NAre you crazy? I don't even know anything about Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你該聽我的話 奎德 我試著讓你別惹上麻煩{\r}\NYou should've listened to me, Quaid. I was there to keep you out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.12,0:22:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}哈利 你這麼做可就錯了 你將我誤認為某個人{\r}\NYou're making a big mistake. You got me mixed up with somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.08,0:22:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不對 兄弟 是你誤認自己是某人{\r}\NUh-uh, pal. You got yourself mixed up with...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}拋 發球{\r}\NAnd pivot... and serve...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}收拍 抽球{\r}\Nand shift... and stroke... and pivot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}發球 收拍 抽球{\r}\NAnd serve... and shift... and stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.37,0:23:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}很好 完美的動做{\r}\NVery good. Perfect form.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.45,0:23:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}發球 收拍 抽球{\r}\NAnd serve... and shift... and stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}親愛的{\r}\NHi, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你在幹什麼  - 剛剛有幾個人想殺我{\r}\N- What are you doing?  - Some men just tried to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}搶匪 你沒事吧{\r}\NMuggers? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.29,0:23:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不 他們是間諜之類的{\r}\NNo, they were spies or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}還有我的同事哈利 他... 快蹲下{\r}\NAnd Harry from work, he was the... Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.33,0:23:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我的同事哈利 他是帶頭大哥  - 道格 冷靜下來 好嗎{\r}\N- Harry from work, he was the boss.  - Take it easy, Doug, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.20,0:23:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}把事情的經過詳細地告訴我 為何會有間諜想要殺你{\r}\NTell me exactly what happened. Why would spies want to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.29,0:23:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我不知道 但和火星有關{\r}\NI don't know. But it had something to do with Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你沒到過火星啊{\r}\NYou've never been to Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.79,0:23:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我知道這聽來很荒唐 但我今天去了瑞可公司...{\r}\NIt sounds crazy, but I went to this Recall place after work...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你跑去找那些腦科殺手  - 先讓我把話說完{\r}\N- You went to those brain butchers?  - Let me finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 他們把你怎麼了  - 我到火星旅遊了一次{\r}\N- What did they do to you?  - I got a trip to Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.20,0:24:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 結果...  - 哦{\r}\N- So what happened...  - Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.16,0:24:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別管瑞可的事 行不行 那些人想殺我啊{\r}\NForget about Recall. Will you? These guys were going to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.58,0:24:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 道格 沒有人想殺你  - 他們想殺我{\r}\N- Doug, nobody tried to kill you.  - They did.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.45,0:24:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}但我殺了他們{\r}\NBut I killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.37,0:24:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}聽我說 親愛的...{\r}\NListen to me, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.12,0:24:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那些瑞可的混蛋弄壞了你的腦袋{\r}\NThose assholes at Recall have fucked up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.25,0:24:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你開始產生偏執的幻想{\r}\NYou're having paranoid delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.45,0:24:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你說這也是幻想嗎{\r}\NYou call this a delusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.83,0:24:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}道格{\r}\NDoug
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.62,0:24:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我要打電話叫醫生來  - 不 別打電話給任何人{\r}\N- Doug, I'm gonna call a doctor.  - Don't. Don't call anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.83,0:24:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你好{\r}\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.95,0:25:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}羅莉 快走 離開這裡{\r}\NLori, go! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.16,0:25:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}羅莉{\r}\NLori?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.54,0:26:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}羅莉 你為什麼要這麼做{\r}\NWhy are you doing this, Lori?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.91,0:26:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}說 我叫你說{\r}\NTalk! I said talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.50,0:26:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我不是你太太  - 你不是才怪{\r}\N- I'm not your wife.  - The hell you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.58,0:26:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我發誓我六個禮拜以前沒見過你{\r}\NI never saw you before six weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.79,0:26:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們的婚姻只是植入的記憶{\r}\NOur marriage is just a memory implant.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.04,0:26:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你認為我是個笨蛋 我記得我們的婚禮{\r}\NYou think I'm stupid? I remember our wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.95,0:26:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那是情報局植入的記憶{\r}\NIt was implanted by the Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.58,0:26:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 戀愛  - 植入的{\r}\N- Falling in love.  - Implanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.41,0:26:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們的朋友 我的工作 八年在一起的時光{\r}\NOur friends, my job, 8 years together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.39,0:26:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}難道這些也全是植入的記憶{\r}\NAll of this was implanted too?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.20,0:26:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}工作是真的 是情報局替你安排的{\r}\NThe job's real. The Agency set it up.
