Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.22,0:39:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}如果事情出了差錯 我如今就得對著自己說話{\r}\NIf things have gone wrong, I'm talking to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.80,0:39:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}而你則得在頭上包著濕毛巾{\r}\Nand you've got a wet towel wrapped around your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.80,0:39:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不管你叫什麼名字 下面這事實包准叫你大吃一驚{\r}\NNow, whatever your name is, get ready for the big surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.72,0:39:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你並不是你 你其實是我{\r}\NYou are not you. You are me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.80,0:39:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別廢話{\r}\NNo shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.18,0:39:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}6B9 6B9 請回答{\r}\NSix-beta-nine, six-beta-nine, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.18,0:39:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你找到他了{\r}\NDid you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.51,0:39:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們掃瞄到廢棄的水泥工廠 發生了一場爆炸{\r}\NWe picked up an explosion at the old cement factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.35,0:39:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 派兩組人過去 咱們在那裡碰頭  - 知道了{\r}\N- Send two units. We'll meet you there.  - Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.43,0:39:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我這輩子都在火星情報部工作{\r}\NAll my life I've worked for Mars Intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.26,0:39:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}替柯黑根做了許多傷天害理的事{\r}\NI did Cohaagen's dirty work.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.64,0:39:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}但幾個禮拜前我遇到一個人 一個女人{\r}\NBut a few weeks ago I met somebody, a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.64,0:39:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}她讓我覺悟到一些事{\r}\Nand I learned a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.80,0:39:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}比方說 我是在助紂為虐{\r}\NLike I've been playing for the wrong team.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.68,0:40:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我現在能做的 就是好好彌補一下過去的罪擎{\r}\NAll I can do now is try to make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.55,0:40:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這個腦袋裡裝的東西 可以讓柯黑根死得很慘{\r}\NThere's enough shit in here to fuck Cohaagen good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.05,0:40:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不幸的是 如果你聽到這段話 就表示他已經先一步整倒了我{\r}\NUnfortunately, if you're listening to this, that means he has got to me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.05,0:40:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}最困難的部份就在此 兄弟{\r}\NHere comes the hard part, old buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.97,0:40:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}從現在起全得靠你了{\r}\NNow it is all up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.26,0:40:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}真是太好了{\r}\NGreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.35,0:40:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你們找到了什麼  - 車上沒有人{\r}\N- What have we got?  - Nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.30,0:40:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 他已經走了  - 我抓到前方有微弱的訊號{\r}\N- He's gone.  - I got a weak signal over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.72,0:40:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}散開 把他找出來{\r}\NSplit up. Find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.30,0:40:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}首先 將你頭裡的追蹤器取出來{\r}\NFirst let's get rid of that bug in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.39,0:40:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}將這東西從箱子裡拿出來 然後插進你的鼻子裡{\r}\NTake this thing out of the case and stick it up your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.22,0:40:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別擔心 它是自動導向的{\r}\NDon't worry. It's self-guiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.18,0:40:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}用力插進去就行了{\r}\NJust shove real hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.18,0:40:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}當你聽到一個碎裂聲 那就是了{\r}\NWhen it crunches, you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.51,0:41:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}將它拉出來{\r}\NJust pull it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.47,0:41:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}但要小心 那也是我的腦袋{\r}\NBe careful. It's my head too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.68,0:41:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我鎖定住他了  - 在上面 咱們上{\r}\N- I've got a lock.  - Up. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.22,0:41:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我的計畫是這樣的...{\r}\NThis is the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.14,0:41:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你到火星上去{\r}\NGet your ass to Mars,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.76,0:41:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}然後到希爾頓飯店 出示一份布魯貝克的證件給櫃檯接待員{\r}\Nthen go to the Hilton and flash the Brubaker ID at the desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.14,0:41:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}如此就行了{\r}\NThat's all there's to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.01,0:41:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}照我的話去做{\r}\NJust do what I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.80,0:41:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}咱們兩個就可以讓那個狗雜種得到應有的制裁{\r}\NAnd we can nail that son of the bitch who fucked you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.93,0:41:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我全靠你了 兄弟{\r}\NI'm counting on you, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.01,0:41:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}可別讓我失望{\r}\NDon't let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.47,0:42:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}正前方{\r}\NStraight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.76,0:42:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}在這裡面{\r}\NIn there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.64,0:42:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那邊{\r}\NThere!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.55,0:42:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那邊{\r}\NThere!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.14,0:42:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那邊{\r}\NThere!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.22,0:42:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}給我{\r}\NWhat? Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.51,0:42:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}到火星上去{\r}\NGet your ass to Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.47,0:43:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 到火星上去  - 他媽的{\r}\N- Get your ass to Mars.  - Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.55,0:43:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}到火星上去 到火星上去{\r}\NGet your ass to Mars... Get your ass to Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.51,0:43:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}歡迎光臨火星聯邦自治區{\r}\NWelcome to the Mars Federal Colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.14,0:43:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}為了各位的健康和舒適 我們建造了圓頂{\r}\NFor your safety and comfort, domes have been installed
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.05,0:43:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}以隔絕外界的真空環境{\r}\Nto protect you from the vacuum outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.68,0:43:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}請不要碰觸外側的窗戶或氣閘{\r}\NPlease do not touch exterior windows or air locks.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.60,0:43:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}由於本地的空氣供應量極為有限 此地全面禁止吸煙{\r}\NAir volume is limited. No smoking is allowed anywhere in the colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.55,0:43:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}下一個{\r}\NNext.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.05,0:44:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}謝謝各位 祝你們在火星的停留期間愉快{\r}\NThank you, and enjoy your stay on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.43,0:44:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}護照呢{\r}\NPassport.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.89,0:44:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}快點 閃一邊去 讓路 退後{\r}\NGet out of the way. Make way! Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.89,0:44:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}柯黑根先生要見你 馬上{\r}\NMr Cohaagen wants to see you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.68,0:44:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}有奎德的消息嗎{\r}\NAny news of Quaid?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.39,0:44:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 自從你追丟他之後就沒有了  - 講話當心點 上尉{\r}\N- Not since you lost him.  - Watch your mouth, Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.43,0:44:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你打算在火星上停留多久  - 兩個禮拜{\r}\N- So how long do you plan to stay?  - Two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.01,0:44:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}看看那上面寫的{\r}\NLook at that shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.47,0:44:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 這他媽的又是什麼  - 火星的人民愛戴寡頭{\r}\N- What the hell's this?  - The Martians love Kuato.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.14,0:44:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他們以為他是華盛頓再世{\r}\NThey think he's fuckin' George Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.30,0:44:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}宰了這混蛋{\r}\NKill the bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.10,0:44:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}沒人知道他到底是誰{\r}\NNobody knows who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.35,0:44:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你有攜帶任何水果或蔬菜嗎{\r}\NHave you brought any fruits or vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.80,0:44:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}兩個禮拜{\r}\NTwo weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.85,0:45:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你說什麼{\r}\NExcuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.39,0:45:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}兩個禮拜{\r}\NTwo weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.01,0:45:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}兩個禮拜{\r}\NTwo weeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.01,0:45:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那不只是普通的塗鴉 叛軍昨晚攻佔了煉製廠{\r}\NIt's not just graffiti. The rebels took over the refinery last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.89,0:45:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}所有的T礦都無法輸出{\r}\NNo terbinium is going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.97,0:45:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}情況還會更嚴重{\r}\NAnd it gets worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.01,0:45:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}奎德{\r}\NQuaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.51,0:45:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 那就是奎德  - 哪裡{\r}\N- That's Quaid!  - Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.26,0:45:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那個女人 把他抓起來 我是說"她"{\r}\NThe woman! Get him... her!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.97,0:45:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}逮捕那女人{\r}\NArrest that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.60,0:45:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}抓住那女人 攔住她{\r}\NGet that woman. Grab her!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.85,0:46:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}接住{\r}\NCatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.18,0:46:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}準備大吃一驚吧{\r}\NGet ready for a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.39,0:47:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 把這該死的門打開  - 我辦不到{\r}\N- Open the goddamn door!  - I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.22,0:47:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}把它打開{\r}\NOpen it!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.60,0:47:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這些門和氣閘是連接在一起的{\r}\NThey're all connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.68,0:47:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}真可怕{\r}\NThat's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.18,0:47:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}而且前幾天柯黑根又提高了空氣的價格{\r}\NA few days ago Cohaagen raised the price of air.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.26,0:47:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}又一次{\r}\NAgain?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.60,0:47:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}地球上的人根本不管我們死活{\r}\NNobody on Earth gives a damn what happens up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.05,0:48:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他們只要T礦 好能夠去打他們那無聊的戰爭{\r}\NThey just want our terbinium so they can fight their war.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.68,0:48:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}對不起 那是什麼{\r}\NExcuse me. What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.76,0:48:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你是指那金字塔礦場{\r}\NYou mean the Pyramid Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.97,0:48:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我在那裡工作過 直到他們在裡面發現外星人留下來的東西{\r}\NI used to work there until they found that alien shit inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.60,0:48:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這不是傳聞而已嗎{\r}\NWell, that's a rumour, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.10,0:48:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你認為如此{\r}\NThink so?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.97,0:48:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}柯黑根先生{\r}\NMr Cohaagen.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.89,0:48:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}長官 你有事找我{\r}\NYou wanted to see me, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.39,0:48:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}瑞克特{\r}\NRichter...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.10,0:49:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你知道我為何如此快樂嗎{\r}\NDo you know why I'm such a happy person?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.22,0:49:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不知道 長官{\r}\NNo, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.68,0:49:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}因為我有全太陽系最棒的工作{\r}\NBecause I've got the greatest job in the solar system.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.10,0:49:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}只要T礦一直生產下去 我就能做任何我想做的事{\r}\NAs long as the terbinium keeps flowing, I can do anything I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.30,0:49:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}任何事{\r}\NAnything
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.30,0:49:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}事實上 我唯一擔心的事只是{\r}\NIn fact, the only thing that I ever worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.55,0:49:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}若有那麼一天 叛軍獲得了勝利 這一切就可能隨之結束...{\r}\Nis that one day, if the rebels win, it all might end...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.14,0:49:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}而你卻要造成這種結果{\r}\Nand you're fucking making it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.80,0:49:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}首先你企圖殺奎德 然後你又讓他逃掉{\r}\NFirst you try to kill Quaid, then you let him get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.85,0:49:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他有我們的人暗中幫助 長官{\r}\NHe had help from our side, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.18,0:49:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這我知道{\r}\NI know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.68,0:49:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 但我以為...  - 誰叫你想{\r}\N- But I thought...  - Who told you to think?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.89,0:49:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我可沒給你足夠的資訊來思考{\r}\NI don't give you enough information to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.01,0:49:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你只要奉命行事就行了{\r}\NYou do what you're told. That's what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.55,0:49:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是 長官{\r}\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.68,0:49:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}現在...{\r}\NNow...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.89,0:49:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}咱們開始來談正事{\r}\NLet's get to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.26,0:50:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們面臨一個難纏的局面{\r}\NWe've got a tricky situation here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.72,0:50:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}寡頭要奎德腦袋裡所知道的東西{\r}\NKuato wants what's in Quaid's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.68,0:50:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}而且他也有可能得到 因為傳聞他有心電感應的能力{\r}\NAnd he might be able to get it, cos they say he's psychic.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.26,0:50:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}而我已想出一個計畫來阻止他成功{\r}\NAnd I have a plan to keep this from happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.80,0:50:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你認為你這回可以好好合作嗎{\r}\NDo you think you could play along?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.51,0:50:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 是的 長官  - 好極了{\r}\N- Yes, sir.  - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.72,0:50:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}否則 我就會取你的狗命{\r}\NCos otherwise, I'll erase your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.47,0:50:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}先生 你要坐計程車嗎 我的車上有雜誌 音樂 威土忌{\r}\NTaxi? You need a taxi, sir? I got magazines, music, whisky.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.55,0:50:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}老兄 要搭計程車嗎 來吧{\r}\NHey, man, you need a cab, man? Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.85,0:50:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}"希爾頓飯店"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.14,0:51:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}下午好 有什麼我能效勞嗎{\r}\NGood afternoon. Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.01,0:51:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是的 麻煩你給我一個房間{\r}\NYes, I would like to have a room, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.97,0:51:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}歡迎再次光臨 布魯貝克先生 你要同一間套房{\r}\NNice to have you back, Mr Brubaker. Would you like the same suite?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.68,0:51:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}當然{\r}\NOh, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.35,0:51:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你似乎有東西放在保管箱裡{\r}\NSeems you've left something in our safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.64,0:51:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}能否麻煩你將它拿來給我{\r}\NCould you get it, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.68,0:51:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們要核對身份{\r}\NIdentification?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.76,0:51:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我這就去拿你房間的鑰匙  - 謝謝{\r}\N- I'll encode your room key.  - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.84,0:52:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}"終極樂園"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.84,0:52:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}"享受好時光 請找梅琳娜"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.47,0:52:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 鑰匙在這裡 西大樓的610號房  - 謝謝{\r}\N- Suite 610 in the east wing.  - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.10,0:52:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我能借用你的筆嗎  - 當然{\r}\N- Could I borrow your pen, please?  - Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.82,0:52:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}"梅琳娜"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.43,0:52:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}謝謝你{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.93,0:52:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}老兄 坐計程車嗎{\r}\NHey, man, you need a cab?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.47,0:52:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這一輛的服務會比你差嗎{\r}\NWhat's wrong with this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.88,0:52:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他可沒有要養五個孩子啊{\r}\NHe ain't got five kids to feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.01,0:52:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你的車在哪兒  - 就在那邊 兄弟{\r}\N- Where's yours?  - Right over there, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.30,0:52:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}嘿 哥們{\r}\NHey! Hey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.55,0:52:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}王八蛋 這是我的客人啊{\r}\NHey, asshole! That's my fare!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.55,0:52:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 一邊涼快去  - 班尼 你這該死的...{\r}\N- Eat this!  - Damn you, Benny!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.55,0:52:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}歡迎光臨火星 兄弟{\r}\NWelcome to Mars, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.26,0:53:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}剛剛那是什麼 意外事件{\r}\NWhat the hell was that, an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.01,0:53:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是反抗軍幹的 咱們快離開此地吧{\r}\NThat's the rebels, man. Let's get outta here...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.47,0:53:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}否則待會就會被捕{\r}\NBefore they arrest us!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.43,0:53:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}反叛軍要的是什麼{\r}\NWhat do the rebels want?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.30,0:53:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}和往常一樣 更多的錢 更多自由 更多空氣{\r}\NThe usual. More money, more freedom, more air.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.85,0:53:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}上哪去{\r}\NSo, where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.18,0:53:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}終極樂園{\r}\NLast Resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.05,0:53:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}才剛到就迫不急待了{\r}\NYou're getting off to an early start.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.01,0:53:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 第一回來火星  - 是的{\r}\N- First time on Mars?  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.39,0:53:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}事實上... 不是 也可說是{\r}\NWell, actually, no. Well, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.80,0:53:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}老天 連自己是否來過火星都弄不清楚{\r}\NThe man don't even know whether he's been to Mars or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.51,0:53:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這就是了 維納斯城{\r}\NVoila. Venusville.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.05,0:53:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}看到中意的貨色沒{\r}\NHa, ha! Hey, you see anything you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.60,0:54:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}車子只能開到此 我們接下來最好用走的{\r}\NWell, this is the end of the line. We'd better walk from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.85,0:54:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我帶你到那地方去{\r}\NI'll show you where.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.93,0:54:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 想知道你的未來嗎  - 過去呢{\r}\N- Do you want to know the future?  - What about the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.64,0:54:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}來吧 就在轉角的地方 就在這巷子裡{\r}\NCome on. It's around the corner, right down this alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.47,0:54:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他們這裡什麼都有{\r}\NThey got everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.18,0:54:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不錯吧{\r}\NNotbad,huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.71,0:54:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}看手相 讀你的心思 你的欲念 你心裡的秘密{\r}\NRead your palm? Your mind? Your aura? Probe the secrets of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.25,0:54:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我打賭我猜得出你的生日{\r}\NI bet I can guess your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.55,0:54:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你是金牛座的 對吧  - 你怎麼猜到的{\r}\N- You're a Taurus, right?  - How did you guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.57,0:54:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 告訴我 所有的通靈人都是...  - 變種{\r}\N- Tell me, are all psychics...?  - Freaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.95,0:54:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}全是變種 是這一帶的特產{\r}\NAfraid so, man. It goes with the territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.07,0:54:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他們怎麼會變成這樣{\r}\NWhat happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.24,0:54:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}廉價的圓頂 又沒空氣來阻擋有害的射線{\r}\NCheap domes, no air to clean the rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.20,0:54:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}咱們到了 終極樂園 你真的要在這間玩嗎{\r}\NSo, this is it. The Last Resort. You sure you want to go in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.24,0:54:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 有何不可  - 我認識另外一家更好的{\r}\N- Why not?  - There's a better place down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.74,0:54:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}女孩子比較乾淨 酒也不摻水{\r}\NThe girls are cleaner, the liquor ain't watered down...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.57,0:54:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是啊 你還可以拿到回扣{\r}\NSure, and you get kickbacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.07,0:54:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}兄弟 我有五個孩子要養啊{\r}\NHey, man, I got five kids to feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.07,0:54:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}帶他們去看牙醫吧{\r}\NTake them to the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.78,0:55:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}謝了 先生 聽我說 我在外面等你{\r}\NHey, thanks, mister! I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.45,0:55:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你慢慢玩好了 我叫班尼{\r}\NYou just take your time. Benny's the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.82,0:55:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 要什麼  - 我找梅琳娜{\r}\N- What do you want?  - I'm looking for Melina.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.95,0:55:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}她現在很忙{\r}\NShe's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.82,0:55:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}找馬麗好了 她有空{\r}\NBut Mary here, she's free.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.40,0:55:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不是免費 親愛的 而是...{\r}\NWell, not free, honey, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.90,0:55:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}有空{\r}\N...available.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.24,0:55:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}謝謝 我還是等梅琳娜好了{\r}\NThanks. I'll wait for Melina.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.70,0:55:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}地球無賴{\r}\NEarth slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.99,0:55:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}問題是 梅琳娜對客人是很挑剔的{\r}\NThing is, friend, Mel's real picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.74,0:55:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}她一向只招待熟客人{\r}\NShe kind of sticks to her regulars.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.11,0:55:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}她會喜歡我的{\r}\NShe'll like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.11,0:55:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}梅琳娜{\r}\NMel!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.49,0:55:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}嘿 梅琳娜{\r}\NHey, Mel!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.07,0:56:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你好 豪瑟{\r}\NHello, Hauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.61,0:56:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}看得出你仍是全身鼓脹如昔{\r}\NStill bulging, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.86,0:56:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 近來都餵養什麼  - 金髮女郎{\r}\N- What you been feeding this thing?  - Blondes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.90,0:56:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那我想它八成沒吃飽{\r}\NI think it's still hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.40,0:56:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}豪瑟 你還有臉跑來這裡{\r}\NYou got a lot of nerve showing your face around here, Hauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.49,0:56:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這句話應該是我說的才對{\r}\NLook who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.57,0:56:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}東尼 別再煩他了{\r}\NHey, Tony, give the big guy a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.45,0:56:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}放輕鬆點 如此才活得久{\r}\NRelax. You'll live longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.86,0:56:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}來吧{\r}\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.90,0:57:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 親愛的 替我去招待東尼好嗎  - 沒問題{\r}\N- Honey, take care of Tony, will you?  - No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.57,0:57:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}如果你應付不了這一個 就喊我一聲{\r}\NIf you need any help with this one, give me a holier.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.61,0:57:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你這狗娘養的{\r}\NYou son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.57,0:57:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你還活著 我都以為你被柯黑根折磨死了{\r}\NYou're alive? I thought that Cohaagen tortured you to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.40,0:57:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我想他大概沒這麼做吧{\r}\NWell, I guess he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.36,0:57:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}而你卻無法傳個口信給我 你難道都沒關心過我的死活{\r}\NAnd you couldn't get me a message? You never wondered what happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.70,0:57:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}豪瑟 謝天謝地 你還活著{\r}\NHauser, thank God you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.11,0:57:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}梅琳... 梅琳娜 梅琳娜{\r}\NMelin... Melina. Melina.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.36,0:57:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 梅琳娜 我有話要告訴你  - 什麼事{\r}\N- Melina, I have to tell you something.  - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.45,0:57:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我已經不記得你了  - 你在胡說些什麼{\r}\N- I don't remember you.  - What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.15,0:57:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我不記得你了{\r}\NI don't remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.40,0:58:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我不記得我們之間的事 我甚至不記得我自己的過去{\r}\NI don't remember us. I don't even remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.90,0:58:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你得了失憶症 你是如何找來這裡的{\r}\NDid you get amnesia? How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.36,0:58:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 豪瑟留給我一張字條  - 豪瑟 你就是豪瑟{\r}\N- Hauser left me a note.  - Hauser? You're Hauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.82,0:58:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}已經不是了{\r}\NNot anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.86,0:58:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我現在是奎德 道格拉斯·奎德{\r}\NNow I'm Quaid. Douglas Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.11,0:58:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}豪瑟 你精神錯亂了{\r}\NHauser, you've lost your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.87,0:58:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我沒有精神錯亂 柯黑根偷了我的記憶{\r}\NI didn't. Cohaagen stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.28,0:58:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他發現豪瑟企圖背叛他 於是將他變成另一個人 變成我{\r}\NHe found out that Hauser switched sides, so he turned him into somebody else: me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.90,0:58:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這故事太玄了{\r}\NThis is too weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.45,0:58:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}再把我丟在地球上 給我一個老婆和一份爛工作{\r}\NHe dumped me on earth with a wife and a lousy job...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.03,0:58:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你說你有老婆 你他媽的結婚了{\r}\NDid you say wife? Are you fucking married?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.03,0:58:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 她其實不是我真正的太太  - 她不是你真正的太太{\r}\N- She wasn't really my wife.  - Oh, she isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.15,0:58:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我可真笨 她是豪瑟的太太{\r}\NHow stupid of me. She was Hauser's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.57,0:58:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 聽著 忘了我提到老婆的事  - 一切都別再說了{\r}\N- Look. Forget that I said wife.  - Let's just forget everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.74,0:58:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我受夠了你和你那些謊言  - 我為何要騙你{\r}\N- I'm sick of hearing your goddamn lies.  - Why would I lie to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.40,0:58:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}因為你仍在為柯黑根工作{\r}\NBecause you're still working for Cohaagen.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.86,0:58:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別胡說了{\r}\NDon't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.15,0:58:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你根本就沒愛過我 豪瑟{\r}\NYou never loved me, Hauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.36,0:58:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你只想利用我 好混進去{\r}\NYou just used me to get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.45,0:59:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}混進什麼裡面{\r}\NInside what?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.49,0:59:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我看你還是走吧{\r}\NI think you'd better leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.65,0:59:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 梅琳娜 豪瑟派我來做某件事  - 我可不會上當{\r}\N- Hauser sent me to do something.  - I'm not falling for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.90,0:59:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他說這腦袋裡裝的東西足以整垮柯黑根{\r}\NHe says there's enough in here to nail Cohaagen for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.24,0:59:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 滾  - 你得幫我恢復記憶{\r}\N- Get out!  - You've got to help me remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.24,0:59:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我叫你滾  - 梅琳娜 求求你{\r}\N- I said, get out!  - Melina, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.53,0:59:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}有人要殺我啊{\r}\NPeople are trying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.20,0:59:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}真的{\r}\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.20,0:59:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}好吧 我這就走{\r}\NAll right, I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.03,0:59:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}寶貝 你讓我恨不得能有三隻手{\r}\NBaby, you make me wish I had three hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.24,0:59:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我想你這兩隻手已經很夠用了{\r}\NI think you're doing just fine with two.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.07,0:59:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}失陪一下 寶貝 咱們待會再聊{\r}\NExcuse me, baby. We'll pick this up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.53,0:59:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}兄弟 你不怎麼持久啊{\r}\NHey, that didn't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.03,0:59:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}聽著 我問你 你玩過變種妞嗎{\r}\NListen. Let me ask you a question. Did you ever fuck a mutant?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.70,0:59:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 送我回飯店去  - 我認識一對變種雙胞胎{\r}\N- Take me to the hotel.  - I know these Siamese twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.24,0:59:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}保證讓你爽歪歪{\r}\NMan, you won't know if you're coming or going.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.61,1:00:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}今天下午四點半時 我簽署一份法令{\r}\NThis afternoon at 4:30pm, I signed an order declaring martial law
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.45,1:00:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}批准在火星聯邦自治區實施戒嚴{\r}\Nthroughout the Mars federal colony.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.70,1:00:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我將不會再容忍任何破壞礦物輸出的行為{\r}\NI will not tolerate any further damage to our mineral export operations.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.61,1:00:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}寡頭先生和他手下的恐怖份子必須明白一件事{\r}\NMr Kuato and his terrorists must understand
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.78,1:00:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他們這種自取毀滅的行為 只會為人民帶來苦難和痛苦...{\r}\Nthat their self- defeating efforts will only bring misery and suffering...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.03,1:00:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 奎德先生  - 什麼事{\r}\N- Mr Quaid?  - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.03,1:00:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我要跟你談談 是關於豪瑟先生的事{\r}\NI need to talk to you about Mr Hauser.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.74,1:00:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你是誰  - 瑞可公司的艾吉馬醫生{\r}\N- Who are you?  - Dr Edgemar from Recall.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.11,1:00:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你是如何找到我的  - 解釋起來有點複雜{\r}\N- How did you find me?  - It's difficult to explain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.45,1:00:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你能開門嗎 我沒有帶武器{\r}\NCould you open the door? I'm unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.57,1:00:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別擔心 我是一個人來的 我可以進去嗎{\r}\NDon't worry. I'm alone. May I come in?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.82,1:00:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你來做什麼{\r}\NWhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.20,1:00:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你聽了後 可能會有點難以接受{\r}\NThis is going to be very difficult for you to accept, Mr Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.61,1:00:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我在聽  - 你此時恐怕不是真的站在這裡{\r}\N- I'm listening.  - You're not really standing here now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.74,1:00:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 醫生 你差點就騙過我了  - 我可是說正經的{\r}\N- Doc, you could have fooled me.  - I'm quite serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.90,1:01:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你不在這裡 我也不在{\r}\NYou're not here and neither am I.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.15,1:01:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這倒新鮮{\r}\NThat's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.65,1:01:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我們又是在哪  - 在瑞可公司{\r}\N- Where are we?  - At Recall.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.90,1:01:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你被綁在一張手術椅上{\r}\NYou're strapped into an implant chair,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.65,1:01:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}而我則透過精神追蹤探針 觀察你的情形{\r}\Nand I'm monitoring you from the psychoprobe console.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.90,1:01:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我明白了 原來我是在做夢{\r}\NAh, I get it. I'm dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.49,1:01:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}而這一切全是貴公司賣給我的刺激的假期的一部份{\r}\NAnd all this is part of the delightful vacation your company has sold me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.86,1:01:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不完全是{\r}\NNot exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.36,1:01:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你目前所經歷的 全是根據我們製作的記憶母帶{\r}\NWhat you're experiencing is a free-form delusion
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.94,1:01:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}所自由創造出來的幻象{\r}\Nbased on our memory tapes
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.61,1:01:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你將不斷地發展出新的情節{\r}\Nbut you're inventing it yourself as you go along.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.70,1:01:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}假設這是我創造出來的幻象 那麼又是誰請你來的{\r}\NIf it is my delusion, who the hell invited you?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.24,1:01:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我被植入這程式 以便發生狀況時能加以補救{\r}\NI've been artificially implanted as an emergency measure.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.03,1:01:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我不得不告訴你 奎德先生 你在手術中出現精神分裂症{\r}\NI'm sorry to tell you this, but you've suffered a schizoid embolism.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.53,1:01:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們無法讓你從幻想中醒來{\r}\NWe can't snap you out of your fantasy,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.90,1:01:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}於是我被派來 看看是否能勸你回到現實世界{\r}\Nand I've been sent in to try to talk you down.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.20,1:01:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}柯黑根付你多少錢來幹這種事{\r}\NHow much is Cohaagen paying you for this?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.45,1:01:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你想想看 你的夢是在植入的過程中開始的{\r}\NThink about it. Your dream started in the middle of the implant procedure.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.74,1:01:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那以後發生的一切 包括追殺 到達火星{\r}\NEverything after that, the chases, the trip to Mars,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.11,1:01:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}住宿於希爾頓飯店 全是瑞可公司提供你的自我旅行情節{\r}\Nthe suite at the Hilton, are elements of your Recall Holiday and Ego Trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.74,1:02:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你付錢來扮演秘密情報員{\r}\NYou paid to be a secret agent.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.20,1:02:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}狗屁 這不過是巧合罷了{\r}\NBullshit. It's coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.78,1:02:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那麼那個女孩呢{\r}\NAnd what about the girl?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.61,1:02:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}褐髮 運動員體型 既放蕩又端莊{\r}\NBrunette, athletic, sleazy and demure?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.32,1:02:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}完全符合你所指定的特徵 這也是巧合嗎{\r}\NJust as you specified. Is that coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.86,1:02:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}她是真的存在的 我在去瑞可之前就夢見過她了{\r}\NShe's real. I dreamt about her before I even went to Recall.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.57,1:02:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}奎德先生...{\r}\NHa, Mr Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.70,1:02:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你知道你這邏輯有多荒唐嗎 你夢見過她 所以她是真的{\r}\NCan you hear yourself? She's real because you dreamed her?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.86,1:02:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 沒錯  - 或許這將能使你信服...{\r}\N- That's right.  - Maybe this will convince you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.95,1:02:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你能把門打開嗎{\r}\NWould you mind opening the door?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.32,1:02:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你去開  - 沒有必要動粗 我來開好了{\r}\N- You open it.  - No need to be rude. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.20,1:02:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}親愛的{\r}\NSweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.99,1:02:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}進來吧 奎德太太{\r}\NCome in, Mrs Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.28,1:02:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我猜你此時也不是真的在此了{\r}\NI suppose you're not here either.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.50,1:02:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我在這裡... 在瑞可公司{\r}\NI'm here... at Recall.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.61,1:03:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我愛你{\r}\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.49,1:03:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是啊 所以你才會想殺我{\r}\NRight. That's why you tried to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.90,1:03:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不 我絕不會做任何傷害你的事{\r}\NNo. I'd never do anything to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.95,1:03:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我要你回到我的身邊{\r}\NI want you to come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.49,1:03:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 狗屁  - 什麼才是狗屁 奎德先生{\r}\N- Bullshit.  - What's bullshit, Mr Quaid?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.82,1:03:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是你的細胞受到精神化學損傷{\r}\NThat you're having a paranoid episode
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.82,1:03:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}而引發一連串偏執的幻想{\r}\Ntriggered by acute neurochemical trauma?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.57,1:03:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}還是你真的是一個來自火星的臥底秘密情報員...{\r}\NOr that you're really an invincible secret agent from Mars,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.61,1:03:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}受到一項星際陰謀的迫害 讓你自以為是個...{\r}\Nwho's the victim of an interplanetary conspiracy to make him think
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.82,1:03:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}卑微的建築工人{\r}\Nhe's a lowly construction worker?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.32,1:03:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別再折磨你自己了 道格{\r}\NStop punishing yourself, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.70,1:03:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你是個正直的好人 你有個深愛著你的美麗妻子{\r}\NYou're a fine, upstanding man. You have a beautiful wife who loves you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.15,1:03:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你還有許多美好的日子要過{\r}\NYour whole life is ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.15,1:03:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}但你得先願意回到現實的世界{\r}\NBut you've got to want to return to reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.11,1:03:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}就算我願意好了... 我又該怎麼做{\r}\NLet's assume I do. Then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.61,1:04:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 把這個吞下去  - 這是什麼{\r}\N- Swallow this.  - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.82,1:04:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}它是一個象徵 表示你願意回到現實的世界{\r}\NIt's a symbol of your desire to return to reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.95,1:04:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}在你的夢裡 你將睡著{\r}\NInside your dream, you'll fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.15,1:04:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}好吧 假設你說的全是事實 這一切全是一場夢{\r}\NAll right, let's say you're telling the truth and this is all a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.99,1:04:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那我大可扣下扳機 反正也不要緊{\r}\NThen I could pull this trigger and it won't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.11,1:04:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 道格 別這麼做  - 這對我不會有什麼差別 道格{\r}\N- Doug, don't.  - It won't make a difference to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.24,1:04:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}但對你卻會有毀滅性的結果 在你的腦海裡 我將喪命{\r}\NBut the consequences to you would be devastating. In your mind I'll be dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.82,1:04:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}在無人引導你走出的情況下 你將陷入永久的精神錯亂{\r}\NWith no one to guide you out, you'll be stuck in permanent psychosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.28,1:04:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}道格 讓艾吉馬醫生幫助你{\r}\NDoug, let Dr Edgemar help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.65,1:04:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}現實世界的牆將整個倒塌{\r}\NThe walls of reality will come crashing down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.90,1:04:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}在前一分鐘裡 你還是拯救叛軍的大英雄{\r}\NOne minute you'll be the saviour of the rebel cause,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.24,1:04:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}但接下來 你又將是柯黑根的心腹爪牙{\r}\Nand the next thing you know you'll be Cohaagen's bosom buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.86,1:04:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你甚至將如你當初所要求的 幻想在太空中發現外星文明{\r}\NYou'll even have fantasies about alien civilisations, as you requested,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.95,1:04:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}但在你終於回到現實世界後 你將被切除腦前葉{\r}\Nbut in the end, back on earth you'll be lobotomised!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.11,1:04:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}所以還是理智點 道格 把槍放下{\r}\NSo get a grip on yourself, Doug, and put down that gun!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.70,1:05:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}很好 現在把那粒膠囊放進嘴裡{\r}\NGood. Now take the pill and put it in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.49,1:05:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}吞下去{\r}\NSwallow it!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.86,1:05:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}吞下去 親愛的{\r}\NGo ahead, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.96,1:05:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}看看你幹了什麼好事 看你幹了什麼好事{\r}\NNow you've done it. Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.29,1:06:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這是回敬你害我跑來火星{\r}\NThat's for making me come to Mars.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.88,1:06:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你知道我有多痛恨這個爛星球{\r}\NYou know how much I hate this fucking planet!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.13,1:06:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}把他銬起來{\r}\NCuff him.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.13,1:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我抓住他了  - 好極了 用服務電梯將他送下來{\r}\N- I got him.  - Bring him down in the service elevator.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.67,1:06:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們走{\r}\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.70,1:07:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}去你的{\r}\NFUCK you!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.21,1:07:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}道格{\r}\NDoug
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.62,1:07:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}親愛的{\r}\NHoney...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.83,1:08:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}親愛的 你不會傷害我 對不對{\r}\NYou wouldn't hurt me, would you, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.08,1:08:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}親愛的 理智點{\r}\NSweetheart, be reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.50,1:08:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}畢竟咱們是夫妻啊{\r}\NAfter all, we're married.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.04,1:08:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}現在離婚了{\r}\NConsider that a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.04,1:08:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}她就是你的老婆{\r}\NThat was your wife?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.70,1:08:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}好一個賤人{\r}\NWhat a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.20,1:08:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}閃一邊去{\r}\NHey, get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.66,1:08:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我還以為你不喜歡我{\r}\NI thought you didn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.50,1:08:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}如果柯黑根要殺你 你就應該沒問題{\r}\NIf Cohaagen wants you dead, you might be OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.29,1:08:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 找到了  - 那麼你是回來向我道歉的{\r}\N- Got it.  - So you've come back to apologise.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.83,1:08:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}寡頭要見你{\r}\NKuato wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.58,1:08:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}快走{\r}\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.45,1:09:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 現在怎麼辦  - 跳{\r}\N- Now what?  - Jump!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.66,1:09:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不 別開槍 你會把圓頂打破的{\r}\NNo! Don't do it! You'll crack the fucking dome!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.00,1:10:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}如果你這麼做 咱們全都會沒命 圓頂會破裂的{\r}\NWhat are you trying to do, kill us? The dome will crack!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.62,1:10:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}走開{\r}\NMove!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.58,1:10:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}計程車{\r}\NTaxi!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.37,1:10:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}梅琳娜 梅琳娜{\r}\NMelina! Melina!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.62,1:10:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 要坐車嗎  - 快 到終極樂園{\r}\N- Need a ride?  - Last Resort. Quick!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.20,1:10:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你們這些人盡在兜圈子{\r}\NYou guys are going in circles.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.70,1:10:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我的天{\r}\NJesus!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.79,1:10:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}快點 你開車{\r}\NCome on! You drive!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.08,1:10:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你們是惹上了什麼麻煩{\r}\NYou guys are in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.29,1:10:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}開車 開車{\r}\NGo! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.79,1:10:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 兄弟 你是想害死我  - 閉嘴 開你的車就行了{\r}\N- What are you trying to do to me?  - Shut up and drive!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.79,1:10:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我還有五個孩子要養啊{\r}\NHey, I got five kids to feed!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.08,1:11:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}糟了{\r}\NShit!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.29,1:11:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 車失靈了  - 停車{\r}\N- No brakes! Ah!  - Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.16,1:11:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你這個白癡{\r}\NYou idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.00,1:11:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你在幹什麼啊{\r}\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.79,1:11:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我的天 現在他們也要殺我了{\r}\NOh, Christ! Now they're after me!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.79,1:11:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}把槍給我{\r}\NGive me that!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.16,1:11:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}滾一邊去{\r}\NGet out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.62,1:12:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}東尼{\r}\NTony!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.70,1:12:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別擋路 快來{\r}\NGet out of the way! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.29,1:12:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}快 快{\r}\NCome on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.83,1:12:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}快{\r}\NQuick!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.04,1:12:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}謝謝你 東尼{\r}\NThank you, Tony.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.70,1:12:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你要... 樂一下嗎{\r}\NHey! You wanna have some fun?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.66,1:12:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他們在哪裡{\r}\NWhere are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.95,1:12:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你在說什麼啊 我不知道{\r}\NWhat are you talking about? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.87,1:13:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}或許你知道{\r}\NMaybe you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.66,1:13:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}把他們都宰了{\r}\NKill them all!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.12,1:13:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}桑蔔琳娜{\r}\NThumbelina!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.37,1:13:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}瑞克特{\r}\NRichter!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.00,1:13:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 柯黑根打電話找你  - 我是瑞克特{\r}\N- A call from Cohaagen!  - Richter here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.50,1:13:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我們壓制住他們了  - 停止戰鬥 將人員撤出{\r}\N- We've got them pinned down.  - Stop fighting and pull out.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.33,1:13:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}但他們藏匿奎德 還保護他{\r}\NBut they've got Quaid. They're protecting him.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.50,1:14:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}好極了 立刻撤出G區{\r}\NPerfect. Get out of Sector G now.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.75,1:14:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別想{\r}\NDon't think.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.37,1:14:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 照辦就是了  - 是 長官{\r}\N- Do it!  - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.95,1:14:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}將人員撤回{\r}\NPull 'em out.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.95,1:14:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}所有人員撤退{\r}\NEverybody, pull out!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.41,1:14:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}快{\r}\NMove!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.79,1:14:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 柯黑根要將這一區封死  - 快來 班尼{\r}\N- Cohaagen's sealing off the area!  - Come on, Benny!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.62,1:15:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}第一代的移民埋骨于此{\r}\NThe first settlers are buried here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.54,1:15:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他們苦幹到死 但財富卻全落到柯黑根手裡{\r}\NThey worked themselves to death, but Cohaagen ended up with all the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.66,1:15:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他替他們建廉價的圓頂 讓他們的後代變成畸形人{\r}\NHe built cheap domes and watched the kids turn into freaks.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.41,1:15:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我見過他們了{\r}\NI saw them.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.75,1:15:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}如果你想呼吸 還得跟他買空氣{\r}\NAnd if you want to breathe, you have to buy his air.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.54,1:15:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}或許你能改變這一切{\r}\NMaybe you can change all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.91,1:15:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我想我的爺爺可能也埋在這裡{\r}\NHey, I think my grandpa might be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.54,1:15:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我能做什麼{\r}\NSo what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.29,1:15:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}寡頭將讓你想起當你還是豪瑟時所知道的事{\r}\NKuato's gonna make you remember some things you knew when you were Hauser.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.12,1:15:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 比方說什麼  - 各種的事{\r}\N- Like what?  - All sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.79,1:15:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 或許你會想起你曾愛過我  - 這倒不需要寡頭的幫忙{\r}\N- Maybe you'll remember you loved me.  - I don't need Kuato for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.04,1:15:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}從什麼時候開始的{\r}\NSince when?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.70,1:16:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別動{\r}\NFreeze!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.54,1:16:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}來吧 梅琳娜{\r}\NCome on, Melina.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.50,1:16:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}寡頭在等了{\r}\NKuato's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.95,1:16:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我找不到我的爺爺 但是...{\r}\NI didn't find Grandpa, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.41,1:16:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我的媽呀{\r}\NOh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.04,1:16:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 這傢伙是誰  - 是他幫助我們逃走的{\r}\N- Who's this?  - He helped us get away.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.29,1:16:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你們無須擔心我 兄弟 我是站在你們這邊的{\r}\NHey, don't worry about me, man. I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.00,1:16:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}原來你是個變種人 是吧{\r}\NYou're a mutant, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.08,1:16:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}好吧 我們走{\r}\NAll right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.54,1:17:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你有試過將門炸開嗎  - 你在這裡等 跟我來{\r}\N- Have you tried ramming down the door?  - You wait here. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.41,1:17:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這麼做也是沒用的{\r}\NIt won't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.29,1:17:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 柯黑根已經將通道減壓  - 那就打通往M區的路{\r}\N- Cohaagen depressurised the tunnels.  - Then drill through to Section M.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.75,1:17:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們辦不到 空氣已快耗盡了{\r}\NWe can't. We're running out of air.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.79,1:17:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們需要援助{\r}\NWe need help.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.95,1:17:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}再忍耐一下 梅琳娜剛剛帶著奎德到達此地{\r}\NSit tight. Melina just got here with Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.62,1:17:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我希望他值得我們如此犧牲{\r}\NI hope he was worth it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.50,1:17:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我也是{\r}\NSo do I.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.50,1:17:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 很高興你們能及時趕來  - 你看來不怎麼高興{\r}\N- I'm glad you made it.  - You don't look glad.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.54,1:17:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}柯黑根封了維納斯城 還停止供應空氣{\r}\NCohaagen sealed up Venusville. He shut off the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.91,1:17:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你一定是知道某些重要的秘密 奎德{\r}\NYou must know something pretty important, Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.16,1:17:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他要你{\r}\NHe wants you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.33,1:17:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}如果我們不把你交出去 到了明早這一區的人都將沒命{\r}\NIf we don't hand you over, everybody in this sector will be dead by morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.83,1:17:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那麼咱們也沒什麼選擇的餘地了{\r}\NThen we don't have much choice. Do we?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.83,1:17:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們不能把他交出去{\r}\NWe can't turn him in.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.66,1:17:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這得讓寡頭來決定 跟我來吧 奎德{\r}\NThat's up to Kuato. Come with me, Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.12,1:17:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}坐{\r}\NSit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.33,1:18:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 寡頭在哪  - 在趕來此地的途中{\r}\N- Where's Kuato?  - On his way.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.29,1:18:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你聽過關於金字塔礦場的傳聞吧{\r}\NYou heard the rumours about the Pyramid Mine?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.83,1:18:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是的{\r}\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.79,1:18:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}柯黑根在那裡面發現了某樣東西 讓他嚇得要命{\r}\NCohaagen found something weird inside and it's got him scared shitless.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.20,1:18:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}什麼東西 外星人{\r}\NWhat? Aliens?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.08,1:18:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你說呢  - 我不知道{\r}\N- You tell me.  - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.95,1:18:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是的 你知道 所以我們才把你弄來這裡{\r}\NYes, you do. That's why we brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.58,1:18:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}柯黑根的大秘密...{\r}\NCohaagen's big secret is buried in that black hole
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.29,1:18:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}就埋在你的腦裡{\r}\Nyou call a brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.95,1:18:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}寡頭將要把它掘出來{\r}\NAnd Kuato's gonna dig it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.91,1:18:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你就是寡頭 對吧  - 錯了{\r}\N- You're Kuato, right?  - Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.45,1:18:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}寡頭是個變種人 當你見到他時可別大驚小怪{\r}\NKuato's a mutant, so don't get upset when you see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.87,1:19:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}奎德先生 你想要什麼{\r}\NWhat do you want, Mr Quaid?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.04,1:19:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}和你要的一樣 恢復記憶{\r}\NThe same as you. To remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.91,1:19:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}但為了什麼{\r}\NBut Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.70,1:19:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 為了能再成為我自己  - 你的所做所為決定你是什麼人{\r}\N- To be myself again.  - You are what you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.37,1:19:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}個人的價值在於他的所做所為{\r}\NA man is defined by his actions...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.75,1:19:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}而不是他的記憶{\r}\Nnot his memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.04,1:19:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}請握住我的雙手{\r}\NPlease take my hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.83,1:19:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}現在 對我敞開你的心靈{\r}\NNow open your mind to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.41,1:19:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}拜託{\r}\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.62,1:19:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}敞開你的心靈...{\r}\NOpen your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.37,1:19:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}敞開你的心靈...{\r}\NOpen your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.08,1:20:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}敞開你的心靈...{\r}\NOpen your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.20,1:20:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}敞開你的心靈...{\r}\NOpen your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.70,1:20:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}敞開你的心靈...{\r}\NOpen your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.95,1:20:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們得在叛軍啟動它之前毀掉它{\r}\NWe should blow the thing up before the rebels turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.37,1:20:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我認為咱們可試著將它啟動 看看會有何結果{\r}\NI say we throw the switch and see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.83,1:20:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 別傻了  - 我們不能冒這種險{\r}\N- Don't be an idiot.  - We can't risk it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.95,1:20:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}引發的連鎖反應 可能會毀掉這星球上所有的T礦{\r}\NThe chain reaction could spread to all the terbinium in the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.95,1:20:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}也就是熔毀 整個星球都可能會熔毀{\r}\NThat means a meltdown, a meltdown on a planetary scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.95,1:21:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你想造這玩意的人沒想到這點{\r}\NDon't you think whoever built this thing thought of that?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.45,1:21:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}誰曉得它們是怎麼想的 它們又不是人類{\r}\NWho knows what the hell they thought? They weren't human.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.62,1:21:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}或許這是個陷阱 或許它們就是要讓這星球熔毀{\r}\NMaybe it's a trap. Maybe they want a meltdown.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.25,1:21:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們甚至不知道這是否還能用{\r}\NWe don't even know if this piece of junk will work.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.50,1:21:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}它的歷史有多久 一百萬年 五十萬年{\r}\NWhat is it? A million? Half a million?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.16,1:21:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 約有五十萬年  - 是五十萬年前造的{\r}\N- About half a million.  - Half a million years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.29,1:21:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們只需不讓寡頭...{\r}\NLet's make sure Kuato...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.08,1:21:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}醒醒 醒醒 快點 醒過來啊{\r}\NWake up! Wake up! Come on, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.83,1:21:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他們找到我們了 該死 我們走吧{\r}\NThey found us! Shit! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.62,1:22:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}快醒醒 清醒過來 快{\r}\NWake up! Snap out of it now! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.50,1:22:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 他們殺進來了 大夥兒撤退  - 梅琳娜{\r}\N- They found us! Everybody out!  - Melina!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.50,1:22:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}快走 走啊{\r}\NGet moving! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.83,1:22:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}走啊{\r}\NGet out!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.54,1:22:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}大夥兒撤退 走啊{\r}\NEverybody out! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.25,1:22:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}到氣閘去 跟我來{\r}\NGet to the air lock! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.33,1:22:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}班尼 快來啊{\r}\NBenny, come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.95,1:22:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 班尼  - 我來了{\r}\N- Benny!  - I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.79,1:23:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}穿上太空衣 我們到外面去{\r}\NPut these spacesuits on! We're going outside!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.08,1:23:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}班尼 快點{\r}\NBenny, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.70,1:23:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}恭喜你 奎德 你終於帶領我們找到了他{\r}\NCongratulations, Quaid. You led us right to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.87,1:23:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你怎能這麼做 你也是個變種人{\r}\NHow can you do this? You're a mutant.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.91,1:23:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我還有四個孩子要養  - 第五個到哪裡去了{\r}\N- I got four kids to feed.  - So what happened to number five?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.58,1:23:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}媽的 你終於抓到我的破綻了{\r}\NOh, shit, man. You got me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.95,1:23:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我根本就還沒結婚{\r}\NI ain't even married.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.70,1:23:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}現在把手舉起來{\r}\NNow put your fucking hands in the air!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.62,1:23:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}奎德...{\r}\NQuaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.20,1:23:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}奎德...{\r}\NQuaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.79,1:23:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別白費力氣了 兄弟 他的算命生涯已經結束了{\r}\NForget it, man. His fortunetelling days are over.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.08,1:23:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}啟動那個反應爐{\r}\NStart the reactor.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.95,1:24:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}解放火星{\r}\NFree Mars.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.95,1:24:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}柯黑根先生想跟你談談{\r}\NMr Cohaagen would like to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.54,1:24:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}原來這就是那位偉人{\r}\NSo this is the great man.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.87,1:24:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}難怪他總能躲過我們的耳目{\r}\NNo wonder he kept out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.95,1:24:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我的好兄弟...{\r}\NWell, my boy...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.45,1:24:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你是個英雄  - 去你的{\r}\N- You're a hero.  - Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.54,1:24:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不必謙虛 如今寡頭已經死了{\r}\NUh? Don't be modest. Kuato is dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.37,1:24:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}叛軍已全部被消滅 而你則是最大的功臣{\r}\NThe resistance is completely wiped out, and you were the key to the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.75,1:24:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他在騙人{\r}\NHe's lying.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.08,1:24:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你這該死的兩面派{\r}\NYou two-faced bastard.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.75,1:24:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別怪他 安琪兒 他的確是無辜的{\r}\NHa, ha. You can't blame him, angel. He's innocent.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.45,1:24:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是這樣的 奎德 我的手下沒有一個能接近寡頭{\r}\NYou see, Quaid, none of my people could get close to Kuato.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.87,1:25:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那些該死的變種人 總是能聞出我們的氣味{\r}\NFucking mutants could always sniff us out.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.79,1:25:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}於是豪瑟和我經過一番思考後 將你創造出來{\r}\NSo Hauser and I sat down and invented you,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.52,1:25:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}一個完美的臥底計畫{\r}\Nthe perfect mole.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.04,1:25:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你根本就是睜眼說瞎話 豪瑟已經背叛了你{\r}\NYou know you're lying. Hauser turned against you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.20,1:25:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們就是要讓你這麼想的{\r}\NThat's what we wanted you to think.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.87,1:25:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}事實是 豪瑟自願來扮演道格·奎德{\r}\NThe fact is, Hauser volunteered to become Doug Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.33,1:25:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}唯有這方法才能騙過那些通靈人{\r}\NIt was the only way to fool the psychics.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.33,1:25:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別說笑了{\r}\NGet your story straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.95,1:25:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}自從我去過瑞可公司後 你手下這些白癡一直在追殺我{\r}\NThis idiot here has been trying to kill me ever since I went to Recall.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.54,1:25:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你怎麼可能要殺你派去臥底的人{\r}\NYou don't kill somebody you're trying to plant.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.91,1:25:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這並非計畫中的一部份 是你自己要去瑞可而壞了事{\r}\NHe wasn't in on it. You set him off by going to Recall.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.91,1:25:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 那麼為何我還活著  - 我們一路上提供你許多幫助{\r}\N- So why am I still alive?  - We gave you lots of help.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.91,1:25:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 比方說班尼  - 這是我的榮幸 兄弟{\r}\N- Benny here.  - My pleasure, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.87,1:25:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那個拿手提箱給你的人 面具 錢{\r}\NThe guy with the suitcase, the mask, the money,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.54,1:25:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}以及豪瑟所留的話 這一切全是我們所安排的{\r}\Nthe message from Hauser, all of that was set up by us.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.54,1:25:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}抱歉 這說法太完美了{\r}\NSorry. Too perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.12,1:25:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}完美個屁{\r}\NPerfect, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.87,1:25:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你在我們還沒來得及派你上場前 就開啟了你的記憶{\r}\NYou pop your memory cap before we can activate you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.62,1:25:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}讓瑞克特到處追殺你 破壞了我花了一年準備的計畫{\r}\NRichter goes hog-wild, screwing up everything I spent a year planning.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.75,1:26:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}老實說 這計畫能成功 連我都感到意外{\r}\NFrankly, I'm amazed it worked.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.66,1:26:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}柯黑根...{\r}\NWell, Cohaagen,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.16,1:26:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我真是服了你 這是我所聽過最精彩的故事{\r}\NI have to hand it to you. It's the best mind-fuck yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.04,1:26:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}先別這麼快就下結論{\r}\NWell, don't take my word for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.54,1:26:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 某個你所信任的人要跟你說話  - 這一回又是誰 我母親{\r}\N- Someone you trust wants to talk to you.  - Who is it this time? My mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.75,1:26:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你好 奎德{\r}\NHowdy, Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.25,1:26:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}如果你聽見這段話 就表示寡頭已死{\r}\NIf you're listening to this, it means that Kuato is dead
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.87,1:26:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}而你也帶領我們找到了他{\r}\Nand you have led us to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.25,1:26:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我就知道你一定不會讓我失望{\r}\NI knew you wouldn't let me down.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.37,1:26:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}抱歉讓你吃了這麼多苦頭 但朋友本來就該互相幫忙的{\r}\NSorry for the shit I've put you through, but hey, what are friends for?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.16,1:26:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我很想祝你永遠快樂 長命百歲 老朋友...{\r}\NI would like to wish you happiness and long life, old buddy,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.54,1:26:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}但不幸的是 這是不可能的{\r}\Nbut unfortunately, this is not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.54,1:26:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}要知道 你佔用的身體是我的 我現在得要回來{\r}\NYou see, it's my body you've got there and I want it back.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.87,1:26:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}抱歉 有借就有還 那身體本來就是我的{\r}\NSorry to be an Indian giver, but I was here first.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.16,1:26:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那麼 永別了 朋友{\r}\NSo adios, amigo.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.87,1:26:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}謝謝你沒讓自己送命{\r}\NAnd thanks for not getting yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.16,1:26:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}或許咱們還會在夢裡見面呢{\r}\NHey, maybe we'll meet in our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.37,1:27:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}誰曉得會怎樣{\r}\NYou never know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.04,1:27:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你們這些混蛋{\r}\NYou bastards!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.25,1:27:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}放開我{\r}\NLet go of me!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.87,1:27:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 準備好了  - 自動{\r}\N- Ready?  - Auto.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.04,1:27:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 全檢查過了  - 全準備好了 長官{\r}\N- Check.  - Ready to go, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.95,1:27:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}放輕鬆點 奎德{\r}\NRelax, Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.25,1:27:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你會喜歡當豪瑟的  - 那傢伙是個該死的混蛋{\r}\N- You'll like being Hauser.  - The guy's a fucking asshole.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.75,1:28:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這不是真的 他是我最要好的朋友之一{\r}\NNot true. He's one of my best friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.04,1:28:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}更何況他有一棟大房子 一輛賓土汽車{\r}\NBesides, he's got a big house and a Mercedes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.04,1:28:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你喜歡梅琳娜 對吧 你今後每晚都可以幹她{\r}\NAnd you like Melina, right? You'll get to fuck her every night.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.16,1:28:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是的 她將成為豪瑟的心肝寶貝{\r}\NThat's right. She's going to be Hauser's babe.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.20,1:28:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我會打爛他的卵蛋{\r}\NI'll bust his balls.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.66,1:28:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不 公主...{\r}\NUh-uh, princess.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.04,1:28:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我們要將你改變一下{\r}\NWe're having you fixed.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.54,1:28:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你將學會尊敬 順從{\r}\NYou're going to be respectful, compliant
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.87,1:28:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}曉得感激 這些都是女人該具有的美德{\r}\Nand appreciative, the way a woman should be.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.16,1:28:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}柯黑根先生 你的電話{\r}\NMr Cohaagen, telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.95,1:28:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是的 什麼事{\r}\NYes? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.75,1:28:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}長官 G區的氧氣已降到最低點{\r}\NThe oxygen level is bottoming out in Sector G.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.54,1:28:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你要我接下來怎麼做{\r}\NWhat do you want me to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.87,1:28:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 什麼也別做  - 但他們支持不到一個鐘頭了 長官{\r}\N- Don't do anything.  - But they won't last an hour, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.04,1:28:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}讓他們去死 可以讓別區的人作為警戒{\r}\NFuck 'em. It'll be a good lesson to the others.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.58,1:28:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別這樣 柯黑根 你已達到你的目的 給這些人空氣吧{\r}\NCome on, you got what you want. Give these people air.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.54,1:28:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我的朋友 再過五分鐘 你就不會關心這些人的死活了{\r}\NMy friend, in five minutes you won't give a shit about the people.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.45,1:29:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}開始吧 醫生{\r}\NFire it up, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.75,1:29:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}對不起 醫生{\r}\NExcuse me, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.95,1:29:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 他將會記得這一切嗎  - 完全不會{\r}\N- Is he gonna remember any of this?  - Not a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.04,1:29:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}真的{\r}\NOh, really?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.75,1:29:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}奎德 我今晚要舉行派對 你可以帶梅琳娜一起來{\r}\NQuaid, I'm having a party tonight. Why don't you and Melina drop by?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.25,1:29:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 提醒他一下 醫生  - 我會的{\r}\N- Remind him, Doc.  - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.91,1:29:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}派對上見了{\r}\NSee you at the party.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.16,1:29:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}別掙扎 你越反抗只會越痛苦{\r}\NKeep still. Fighting just makes it hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.45,1:29:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}如果你不安靜下來 會精神錯亂的{\r}\NIf you don't keep still, you'll end up psychotic.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.45,1:30:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不{\r}\NHey, don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.87,1:30:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}梅琳娜 支持住{\r}\NMelina, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.45,1:30:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你還好吧 你仍是原來的你嗎{\r}\NAre you all right? Are you still you?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.87,1:30:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我也不怎麼確定 親愛的 你想呢{\r}\NI'm not sure, dear. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.16,1:30:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}咱們快離開這裡吧{\r}\NLet's get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.79,1:31:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你得做個決定才行 長官{\r}\NYou have to make a decision, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.62,1:31:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}殺了他{\r}\NKill him.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.12,1:31:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}也該是時候了{\r}\NIt's about goddamn time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.41,1:32:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你要上哪去  - 去找那反應爐{\r}\N- Where are you going?  - To the reactor.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.20,1:32:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 什麼反應爐  - 在礦坑裡的那個 快點{\r}\N- What reactor?  - The one in the mines. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.00,1:32:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那些人都快死了啊 奎德 快停下來 我們得給他們空氣{\r}\NPeople are dying, Quaid! Stop! We've got to get air!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.12,1:32:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那反應爐能製造空氣 這就是柯黑根的大秘密 我們走{\r}\NThe reactor makes air. That's Cohaagen's secret. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.41,1:32:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這個反應爐又是從哪來的{\r}\NWhere's this reactor come from?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.00,1:32:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 外星人造的  - 外星人{\r}\N- Aliens built it.  - Aliens?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.12,1:32:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 你確定它有用嗎  - 它就在前面{\r}\N- Are you sure about this?  - It's just up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.12,1:32:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}被封住了{\r}\NWhat the hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.79,1:33:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}奎德 奎德 你還記得我吧{\r}\NQuaid! Hey, Quaid, you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.00,1:33:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}是班尼 班尼就是我的名字{\r}\NBenny! Benny's the name!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.50,1:33:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這個厲害{\r}\NOh, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.79,1:33:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我要把你們開膛破肚 我要把你們絞成肉泥{\r}\NI'm gonna drill you, sucker! I'm gonna grind you up!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.66,1:33:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我來了{\r}\NHa-ha! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.08,1:33:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我來找你了 寶貝{\r}\NI'm coming for you, baby!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.41,1:34:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這他媽的怎麼回事{\r}\NWhat the fuck is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.00,1:34:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這個該死的火星廢物{\r}\NDamn this piece of Martian junk!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.50,1:34:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}奎德 我要把你壓扁{\r}\NHey, Quaid, I'm gonna squash you!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.20,1:34:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}班尼 嘗嘗這個吧{\r}\NBenny, here!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.29,1:34:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你他媽的在哪裡{\r}\NWhere the fuck are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.58,1:34:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我鑽死你{\r}\NScrew you!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.41,1:34:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 奎德 快到這邊來  - 什麼事{\r}\N- Quaid, get over here!  - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.29,1:34:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 這邊打通了一個缺口  - 我就知道{\r}\N- There's an opening.  - I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.91,1:35:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}這整個東西就是個以T礦製成的反應爐{\r}\NThis whole thing is one big reactor made out of terbinium.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.29,1:35:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}柯黑根知道它可以製造氧氣 但那混蛋卻不肯將它啟動{\r}\NCohaagen knows it makes air. The bastard won't turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.70,1:35:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}當然了 如果火星有了大氣層 他就無法再統治了{\r}\NOf course not. If Mars had an atmosphere, he'd lose control.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.20,1:35:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}看到那下面沒{\r}\NSee down there?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.70,1:35:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}那是一條冰河{\r}\NIt's a glacier.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.20,1:35:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}整個火星的核心都是冰{\r}\NThe whole core of Mars is ice.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.41,1:35:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}反應爐把冰融化 就會釋放出氧氣來{\r}\NThe reactor melts it and it releases the oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.79,1:35:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}來吧{\r}\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.20,1:35:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 足夠讓所有的人呼吸  - 當然{\r}\N- Enough for everyone to breathe?  - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.29,1:35:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}足以供給整個星球使用{\r}\NEnough for the whole planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.29,1:36:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}如果咱們能及時將它啟動的話{\r}\NIf we turn it on in time.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.20,1:36:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}上 快{\r}\NCome on. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.12,1:36:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}慢著{\r}\NHold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.70,1:36:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}開槍{\r}\NNow!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.95,1:37:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}狗娘養的{\r}\NSon of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.08,1:37:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}快退開{\r}\NMove!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.50,1:37:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}他身上有全息圖裝置{\r}\NHe's got a hologram!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.50,1:38:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你們以為這是真的奎德嗎 是真的{\r}\NYou think this is the real Quaid? It is.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.62,1:39:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我要死也要拉你墊背{\r}\NYou're coming with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.58,1:39:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}派對上見了 瑞克特{\r}\NSee you at the party, Richter.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.08,1:40:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 別碰那東西 退後  - 你怕什麼{\r}\N- Don't touch that! Get back!  - What are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.66,1:40:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 將它啟動啊  - 這是不可能的{\r}\N- Turn it on.  - Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.12,1:40:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}一旦連鎖反應產生 這星球上的T礦全將被毀{\r}\NOnce the reaction starts, it'll spread to all the terbinium in the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.41,1:40:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}整個火星也將熔毀{\r}\NMars will go into global meltdown.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.83,1:40:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}所以外星人才從未使用過它{\r}\NThat's why the aliens never turned it on.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.50,1:40:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你以為我會相信你嗎{\r}\NAnd you expect me to believe you?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.62,1:40:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}誰在乎你相不相信 再過30秒你就沒命了{\r}\NWho gives a shit what you believe? In 30 seconds you'll be dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.41,1:40:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}然後我將炸了這個地方 回家去吃麥片{\r}\NThen I'll blow this place up and be home in time for cornflakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.33,1:40:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}我本來也不希望見到這種結局 我要豪瑟回來 但事與願違...{\r}\NI didn't want it to end this way. I wanted Hauser back. But no.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.62,1:41:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你偏要當奎德{\r}\NYou had to be Quaid!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.79,1:41:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}- 我本來就是奎德  - 你什麼也不是{\r}\N- I am Quaid.  - You're nothing!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.29,1:41:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}你什麼人也不是 只是一場愚笨的夢{\r}\NYou're nobody! You're a stupid dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.54,1:41:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}所有的夢都是會結束的{\r}\NWell, all dreams come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.29,1:42:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}梅琳娜 別鬆手{\r}\NMelina, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.70,1:42:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fn宋體}不 別這麼做 我們全都會死{\r}\NDon't do it! We'll all die!
